summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2002 DODGE STRATUS.  THE CONTACT STATED THAT THERE WERE TWO 3-INCH CRACKS, AND TWO 5-INCH CRACKS IN THE DASHBOARD.  AS OF FEBRUARY 25, 2008, THE DEALER HAD NOT INSPECTED THE VEHICLE.  THE MANUFACTURER STATED THAT THERE WERE NO RECALLS ASSOCIATED WITH THE VEHICLE.  THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 60,000 AND CURRENT MILEAGE WAS 70,740.
